%pyspark 

DATA_PATH = "/Users/beom/Workspace/DataEngineering/Final Project/Data"

enrollment_df = (
    spark.read
        .option("header", "true")
        .option("delimiter", ",")
        .csv(DATA_PATH + "/enrollment.csv")    
        .withColumn("enrollment_id", col("enrollment_id").cast("int"))
)
print("enrollment_df", enrollment_df.columns)

log_df = (
    spark.read
        .option("header", "true")
        .option("delimiter", ",")
        .csv(DATA_PATH + "/log.csv")
        .withColumn("date", col("time").cast("date"))
        .withColumn("enrollment_id", col("enrollment_id").cast("int"))
)
print("log_df", log_df.columns)

date_df = (
    spark.read
        .option("header", "true")
        .option("delimiter", ",")
        .csv(DATA_PATH + "/date.csv")
        .withColumn("from", col("from").cast("date"))
        .withColumn("to", col("to").cast("date"))
)
print("date_df", date_df.columns)

object_df = (
    spark.read
        .option("header", "true")
        .option("delimiter", ",")
        .csv(DATA_PATH + "/object.csv")
)
print("object_df", object_df.columns)

truth_df = (
    spark.read
        .option("header", "true")
        .option("delimiter", ",")
        .csv(DATA_PATH + "/truth.csv")
        .select(
            col("eid").alias("enrollment_id"),
            col("result").cast("boolean").alias("dropout")
        )
        .withColumn("enrollment_id", col("enrollment_id").cast("int"))
)
print("truth_df", truth_df.columns)

%pyspark

def flatmap_enrollment(row):
    df = row["from"]
    dt = row["to"]
    dates = []
    while df != dt:
        dates.append(df)
        df = df + datetime.timedelta(days=1)
    dates.append(df)
    
    return [Row(**{
        "enrollment_id": row["enrollment_id"],
        "date": date,
        "from": row["from"],
    }) for date in dates]
    
flat_enrollment_df = (
    enrollment_df
        .join(date_df, ["course_id"])
        .rdd.flatMap(flatmap_enrollment).toDF()
        .withColumn("dday", datediff("date", "from"))
        .select("enrollment_id", "dday", "date")
        .orderBy("enrollment_id", "dday", "date")
)

print("flat_enrollment_df", flat_enrollment_df.columns)

paragraphs.title: feature 1. enrollment의 date별 event count
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

event_values = ["access", "wiki", "navigate", "discussion" ,"problem", "video", "page_close"]
source_values = ["server", "browser"]

df = (
    log_df
        .groupBy("enrollment_id", "date")
        .agg(
            count("*").alias("c_log"),
            *(
                agg_count_by_col_values("event", event_values, ["c_" + v for v in event_values]) +
                agg_count_by_col_values("source", source_values, ["c_" + v for v in source_values])
            )
        )
)

feature1_df = (
    flat_enrollment_df
        .join(df, ["enrollment_id", "date"], "left")
        .na.fill(0)
        .orderBy("enrollment_id", "dday")
)

feature1_df.repartition(1).write.mode("ignore").parquet(DATA_PATH + "/feature1")
feature1_df = spark.read.parquet(DATA_PATH + "/feature1")
print("feature1_df" + str(feature1_df.columns))

paragraphs.title: Save feature1 pkl
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

df = (
    feature1_df
        .filter(col("c_log") > 0)
        .withColumn("year", substring(col("date"), 0, 4).cast("int"))
        .withColumn("month", substring(col("date"), 6, 2).cast("int"))
        .withColumn("day", substring(col("date"), 9, 2).cast("int"))
        .drop("date")
)
feature_cols = df.columns
feature_cols.remove("enrollment_id")
feature_cols.remove("dday")
assembler = VectorAssembler(inputCols=feature_cols, outputCol="feature")
df = assembler.transform(df).drop(*feature_cols).orderBy("enrollment_id", "dday")
df = df.groupBy("enrollment_id").agg(collect_list(struct("dday", "feature")).alias("features")).orderBy("enrollment_id")

feature1 = {}
for r in df.collect():
    feature1[r.enrollment_id] = [[f.dday, f.feature] for f in r.features]

with open(DATA_PATH + "/feature1.pkl", "wb") as f:
    pickle.dump(feature1, f)
